CHROMNITWEET PRIVACY POLICY

Chromnitweet is a Twitter client installed on your computer as a Chrome
extension.  All communication performed in Chromnitweet is directly between
Twitter and its users.  Chromnitweet does not rely on, or have access to, any
third-party servers.  Therefore, Chromnitweet and its creators do not, and can
not, record, keep or access any data on any of its users.

CHANGES TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, we advise you to
review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes
by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. These changes are effective
immediately, after they are posted on this page.

CONTACT US

Questions and suggestions about this privacy policy are welcome by email at
caseydwyer@gmail.com.
